00:19:42,720 --> 00:19:44,520
because we have a sense at this
point which groups are going

511
00:19:44,520 --> 00:19:45,800
to have the most
trouble getting started.

512
00:19:45,800 --> 00:19:47,990
And there are some groups where
once you get them started,

