you can scan the room

525
00:20:11,030 --> 00:20:14,690
and see very quickly how far
each student or group has

526
00:20:14,690 --> 00:20:17,230
gotten on these problems, which
student is holding the pen

527
00:20:17,230 --> 00:20:19,860
and are explaining.

528
00:20:19,860 --> 00:20:21,790
By the time this
period has ended

529
00:20:21,790 --> 00:20:23,700
where they've been
working on these problems,

