00:23:23,850 --> 00:23:26,330
And I think this tool
in particular, transfers

613
00:23:26,330 --> 00:23:27,500
very broadly very easily.

614
00:23:27,500 --> 00:23:29,480
It doesn't have to be a math
class or a physics course.

